  "message": "\ud83c\udf31 Remove unused @headlessui/react dependency (#365)\n\nThe @headlessui/react package was listed as a dependency but never\nimported in the codebase. Removing it reduces bundle size and\nmaintenance overhead.\n\nNote: Other dependencies flagged by Auto-QA are actually needed:\n- react-is: required by @react-three/drei\n- sucrase: required by tailwindcss\n- @netlify/blobs: used in netlify/functions/presence.mts\n\nFixes #362\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
